    'Table layout is reverse compared to deaths/kills table.\n\n1 row per player, 46 bytes per row, 1 byte per upgrade.\n\n*****ALL BW upgrades addresses generated automatically in Eud Editor 2 0.17.9.7 are wrong*****\n*****Please follow contents below*****\n\nOffset: `15 * Player + Offs`\n\n**BW Upgrades:**\n* ID 00 +0 unknown upgrade46\n* ID 01 +1 argus jewel (corsair +50)\n* ID 02 +2 unknown upgrade48\n* ID 03 +3 arugs talisman (DA +50)\n* ID 04 +4 unknown upgrade50\n* ID 05 +5 caduceus reactor (medic +50)\n* ID 06 +6 chitinous plating\n* ID 07 +7 anabolic synthesis\n* ID 08 +8 charon booster\n* ID 09 +9 unknown upgrade55\n* ID 10 +10 unknown upgrade56\n* ID 11 +11 unknown upgrade57\n* ID 12 +12 unknown upgrade58\n* ID 13 +13 unknown upgrade59\n* ID 14 +14 unknown upgrade60',
