    'Detects if a unit have been infected with a parasite (*256).\n\nFlags connected to player ID. Value is a sum of:\n* P1: 256\n* P2: 512\n* P3: 1024\n* P4: 2048\n* P5: 4096\n* P6: 8192\n* P7: 16384\n* P8: 32768',
